title: Clara Petch, Student-Athlete of the Week
text:
Clara Petch, Colorado Academy
Height: 5-foot-9.
Weight: 120 pounds.
Age: 17. Born: Oct. 3, 1998, in Nottingham, U.K.
High school sport: Field hockey (forward with 17 goals and 10 assists).
Grade-point average: 3.98.
Class: Senior.
My family: Parents Mandy and Michael.
Planned career: Law.
iPhone or other: iPhone.
Twitter handle: No account.
Three apps I open every day: Instagram, SnapChat, YouTube.
Computer or TV? Computer.
Energy drink or smoothie? Smoothie.
Pizza or burrito? Pizza.
Best prep sports moment so far: Being part of a team with such great tradition and that has been so successful. (The Mustangs have won the past three state titles.)
